"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-12-olympic-breakdancing-judge-reveals-raygun-scored-zero-21404802\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"AnOlympicbreakdancing judge admits Raygun's level 'was not as high other competitors' after she failed to score a single point inParis.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 41, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.556695586455254e-21, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian B-girl Rachael 'Raygun' Gunn scored zero in all three of her heats during the event on Friday but became a global sensation after her performance went viral onsocial media.\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9975698207390675, \"rank\": 0.0023431398610927363, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 155, \"end\": 162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999616229623, \"rank\": 3.8365744850709e-08, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 164, \"end\": 170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.556695586455254e-21, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old was unable to impress the five-strong judging panel with her moves, which included the now-infamous kangaroo hop.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Olympic breaking head judge, Martin Gilian, who performs as MGbility, has defended Raygun's performance and insists her score was impacted by the quality of her rivals on stage.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 491, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"score\": 0.5772397150946148, \"rank\": 0.7323825242720554, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.556695586455254e-21, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I feel personally very sorry,' MGbility said.\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The breaking and hip-hop community definitely stands behind her.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was just trying to bring something new, something original and something that represents her country.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We stay with her.\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have five criteria in the comparative judging system.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just her level was maybe not as high as the other competitors.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Again, we are using a comparative judging system.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her competitors were just better but it does not mean that she did really bad.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She did her best.'\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raygun finished above Manizha Talash, who was disqualified, but MGbility insists the Australian, who is a university lecturer in Sydney, brought 'something new to the table'.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manizha\", \"score\": 0.999999999973852, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Manizha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manizha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manizha\"}, {\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Talash_(1969_film)\", \"score\": 0.8586826980553357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Talash\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Talash_(1969_film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Talash_(1969_film)\"}, {\"begin\": 1237, \"end\": 1247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9975698207390675, \"rank\": 0.0023431398610927363, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1281, \"end\": 1287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9991693427648427, \"rank\": 0.0007447146614523034, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She was representing Australia and Oceania and did her best,' MGbility said.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1364, \"end\": 1371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\", \"score\": 0.9728372365552652, \"rank\": 0.027920772827758494, \"text\": \"Oceania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She won the Oceania qualifier officially.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\", \"score\": 0.9728372365552652, \"rank\": 0.027920772827758494, \"text\": \"Oceania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If some people are wondering how she got into the Olympic Games, she qualified from her region.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Unfortunately for her, the other b-girls were better.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why she did not score any votes in her rounds.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Breaking is all about originality and bringing something new to the table from your country or region and this is exactly what Raygun was doing.\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1785, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.556695586455254e-21, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She got inspired by her surroundings, which in this case, for example, was you know, kangaroo, the animal.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'For breaking, when you look for innovations or originality, you always search outside of dancing.\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Martial arts, how the animals move, anything.'\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Pilot killed after stolen helicopter cr